HEADWORD: Groomer
<hw>Groom"er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who, or that
which, grooms horses; especially, a brush rotated by a flexible or
jointed revolving shaft, for cleaning horses.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

